{"tid":505749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【過份】變性人遭6男性侵整夜　「他們用槍插進我腸子」","createTime":"2017-12-21T12:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T13:30:17.000Z","uid":10958,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"45398e8d13e14695a1e49c3355cff04130627249","tid":505749,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>【過份】變性人遭6男性侵整夜　「他們用槍插進我腸子」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/12/21/3509354/1263208_360p.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F3509354%2F1263208_360p.mp4&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=0804107b\" target=\"_blank\">https://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/12/21/3509354/1263208_360p.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(新增配音影片)<br />\n<br />\n慘痛而堅強！本名克林頓（Clinton Jessica Earle）的澳洲變性人克蘿伊（Chloe），經歷霸凌、家人厭惡、病魔攻擊後，終於成為一名女人，卻又在約會過程中遭到6名男子輪番性侵，甚至被槍從肛門插到腸子，但她再次堅強撐了過來，她表示自己終於成為女人，「我每天都要活著醒來」。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，克蘿伊從5歲開始就覺得自己與常人不同，上學期間屢屢遭到同學白眼及霸凌，終於她決定在20歲變性成為女人，但除了母親外沒有人支持，家人、朋友都與她斷絕往來，還她仍然堅持注射荷爾蒙性。想不到孤獨無援的克蘿伊又被診斷出白血病，她開始接受化療，並隱瞞情況繼續上班，奇蹟地戰勝了病魔。<br />\n<br />\n克蘿伊似乎時來運轉，荷爾蒙注射起了作用，臀部更翹、胸部隆起，身體開始跟上女人的心靈，她還與男網友約會，想不到這場約會又成了苦難。她被帶到一間狹小的旅館，發現房間裡擠了6名男子，然後她被輪流性侵了一夜，最後「他們用一把鋸斷的槍插進我的腸子」。她表示自己被發現時差點就死了，「我的心跳每分鐘只剩9下」。<br />\n<br />\n所幸克蘿伊再次渡過難關，如今33歲的她已經成為一名堅強的女人，她表示身為變性人，日常生活中仍然有著無數挑戰，而最令她遺憾的是無法擁有自己的小孩，但她不後悔，她很高興自己有了想要外貌，「我每天都要活著醒來」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n出版:0002<br />\n更新:1205<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171221/1263208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263208&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=c4cf1d49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171221%2F1263208&h=6e6cec6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171221/1263208</a>"},{"pid":"942b995038452a4435f5edf8de2863870fa02e03","tid":505749,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2615490ad488ae0d8b9ea4d39986ebbe5f8caca1","tid":505749,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"槍？？"},{"pid":"57a25b87c5f60a97c8e92a69c40814c7b751f7ac","tid":505749,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>槍？？</blockquote><br />\n唐家"},{"pid":"890974a278c44cbe31c7bcc5afda1f84b04d6ae7","tid":505749,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cab67e0241c741ed92c39172dd22cad9086ba3d5","tid":505749,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"yooooooooo!"},{"pid":"b3fc3a45ba1505a0aaba19a48ff057853688a895","tid":505749,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"賤人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2ed30b50acb869d1894faa74e74311274a88b2","tid":505749,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>槍？？</blockquote><br />\n唐家</blockquote><br />\n早知用奪命書生"},{"pid":"8348686ca9211555c4d00b25d581f81979c04c41","tid":505749,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}